'''2015年[[公告牌音乐奖|公告牌音乐奖]]'''（{{lang-en|2015 Billboard Music Awards}}）是一项音乐颁奖典礼，于2015年5月17日在[[拉斯维加斯|拉斯维加斯]]{{tsl|en|MGM Grand Garden Arena|米高梅豪华花园剧场}}举行，由[[ABC|ABC]]直播，[[克莉丝汀·泰根|克莉丝汀·泰根]]和[[卢达克里斯|卢达克里斯]]主持。

[[泰勒·斯威夫特|泰勒絲]]十四项提名有八项获奖，包括最佳艺人、最佳女艺人和最佳公示牌二百强专辑榜专辑（《[[1989_(泰勒·斯威夫特专辑)|1989]]》）。其他获奖者包括[[山姆·史密斯_(歌手)|山姆·史密斯]]、[[伊基·阿塞莉娅|伊基·阿塞莉娅]]和[[法瑞尔·威廉姆斯|法瑞尔·威廉姆斯]]。[[梅根·崔娜|梅根·崔娜]]、[[单向乐队|单向乐队]]、[[杰森·阿尔登|杰森·阿尔登]]、[[约翰·传奇|约翰·传奇]]和[[安德鲁·霍齐尔·伯恩|霍齐尔]]分获两项大奖<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/events/bbma-2015/6524277/billboard-music-awards-2015-finalists |title=Billboard Music Awards 2015: See the Full List of Finalists |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |date=April 7, 2015 |accessdate=April 7, 2015 |archive-date=2015-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409005544/http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/bbma-2015/6524277/billboard-music-awards-2015-finalists |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/bbma/6568580/billboard-music-awards-2015-winners-list |title=Billboard Music Awards 2015: See the Full Winners List |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |date=May 17, 2015 |accessdate=May 17, 2015 |archive-date=2016-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202202206/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/bbma/6568580/billboard-music-awards-2015-winners-list |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 泰勒·斯威夫特在典礼上首次献上单曲《[[敌对_(歌曲)|敌对]]》的音乐录影带<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6560641/taylor-swift-catastrophe-poster-bad-blood-video|title=Taylor Swift to Debut 'Bad Blood' Video During 2015 Billboard Music Awards|work=billboard.com|date=May 7, 2015|accessdate=2015-05-22|archive-date=2015-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150510014440/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6560641/taylor-swift-catastrophe-poster-bad-blood-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[玛丽亚·凯莉|玛丽亚·凯莉]]自1998年以来首次在公告牌舞台上表演<ref name="mariah">{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6553980/mariah-carey-2015-billboard-music-awards |title=Mariah Carey to Perform at 2015 Billboard Music Awards |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |date=May 5, 2015 |accessdate=May 6, 2015 |archive-date=2015-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150506204314/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6553980/mariah-carey-2015-billboard-music-awards |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[布兰妮·斯皮尔斯|布兰妮·斯皮尔斯]]也在蛰伏四年后重返公告牌舞台<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2015/may/18/taylor-swift-winner-calvin-harris-2015-billboard-music-awards|title=Taylor Swift is big winner at 2015 Billboard music awards|date=17 May 2015|work=Guardian|accessdate=19 May 2015|archive-date=2015-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150521013834/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2015/may/18/taylor-swift-winner-calvin-harris-2015-billboard-music-awards|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/05/18/entertainment/billboard-music-awards-2015-swift-smith-feat/|title=Billboard Music Awards 2015 recap: Taylor Swift, Sam Smith clean up|date=17 May 2015|work=CNN|accessdate=19 May 2015|archive-date=2015-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150523050221/http://edition.cnn.com/2015/05/18/entertainment/billboard-music-awards-2015-swift-smith-feat/|dead-url=no}}</ref>	。[[芒果TV|芒果TV]]在中国大陆地区独家直播本届颁奖礼<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hunantv.com/v/4/150739/f/1520064.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-06-07 |archive-date=2015-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150602190927/http://www.hunantv.com/v/4/150739/f/1520064.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

